---
import Button from "./Button.astro";

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-navy via-navy-light to-navy py-20 sm:py-24">
  <!-- Decorative background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-teal rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-72 h-72 bg-teal rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/3"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div class="animate-fade-up max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
        お気軽にご相談ください
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
        経営に関するお悩みや課題について、まずはお気軽にご相談ください。<br class="hidden sm:inline" />
        貴社に最適なソリューションをご提案いたします。
      </p>
      <div class="pt-2">
        <Button variant="secondary" size="lg" href={`${base}contact/`}>
          お問い合わせはこちら
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
